name: ANDREW LESSMAN Essential Omega-3 Unflavored - 180 Softgels - Ultra-Pure, High Potency Omega-3 Oils. High DHA, No Stomach Upset, No Contaminants, No Mercury. Small Easy to Swallow Softgels
feature_bullets: THE ULTRA-PURE, HIGH POTENCY BLEND OF OMEGA-3 OILS, to support the health of your Heart, Brain and Eyes – Delivers the most active, natural triglyceride form and NOT as inferior ethyl esters like so many other brands. Also delivers vital DHA, which is essential for brain and eye health. Andrew Lessman’s Essential Omega-3 allows you to enjoy all the benefits of fish oil with NO mercury, NO contaminants, and NO stomach upset.,SUPERIOR 100% PURE BIO-ACTIVE INGREDIENTS – Concentrated, ultra-pure fish oil provides Omega-3’s including DHA-Docosahexaenoic Acid, EPA-Eicosapentaenoic Acid and DPA-Docosapentaenoic Acid, along with SDA (Stearidonic Acid) from Ahiflower Oil. Contains NO Milk / Dairy-Free, Gluten Free; NO soy, yeast, corn, wheat, sodium, salt, sugar, starch, emulsifier, wax, binder, filler, excipient, lubricant, coating, diluent, flowing agent, color, sweetener or preservative.,UNSURPASSED PURITY, QUALITY, & EFFICACY. WON’T UPSET YOUR STOMACH! – For 40+ years ProCaps products have contained NO additives of any kind. NO binders, fillers, lubricants, stabilizers, flowing agents, preservatives or artificial colors. Easy-to-swallow capsules (NO tablets) deliver only the MOST bioactive vitamins, minerals & ingredients for fast, complete absorption & maximum effectiveness. Non-acidic formula is gentle even on most sensitive stomachs.,MANUFACTURER DIRECT & MADE IN USA – ProCaps formulates, manufactures, and packages ALL of its products in ProCaps’ own laboratory and manufacturing plant in Nevada, USA. Unlike other nutritional supplement brands that utilize contract manufacturers, ProCaps controls every aspect of its products – from formulation design to ingredient sourcing, production techniques, and quality control – making ProCaps’ supplements the purest, safest, and most effective all-natural supplements available.,ETHICAL & ECO-FRIENDY. ZERO CARBON FOOTPRINT – Uniquely committed to your health and the health of the planet, ProCaps’ facilities are 100% Solar Powered with a Zero Carbon Footprint and an LEED GOLD green building status. ALL ProCaps bottles are made from 100% recyclable post-consumer resin. Plus, Andrew Lessman and ProCaps are the largest donor of prenatal vitamins in the world (over 1 billion capsules donated to date). ProCaps, the Informed Choice for Nutritional Supplements.

name: Life Extension Super Omega-3 Plus EPA/DHA Fish Oil, Sesame Lignans, Olive Extract, Krill & Astaxanthin - Heart, Brain & Joint Health Support - Gluten-Free, Non-GMO - 120 Softgels
feature_bullets: A FRESH & PURE FISH OIL - Our formula is made with a wild fish oil concentrate derived from South Pacific Ocean anchovy. It's caught and processed within hours of harvest in a marine mammal-friendly fishery in Chile.,GOOD FOR HEART & MIND - You'll get optimal doses of EPA and DHA omega-3 fatty acids with our formula, which supports cardiovascular and cognitive health. But that's just the beginning. We were inspired by the Mediterranean diet, which is associated with heart health and an increased life span. So we also include potent olive polyphenols and sesame lignans for additional health benefits.,KRILL OIL & ASTAXANTHIN - Our formula offers even more benefits with krill oil and astaxanthin. In clinical studies, krill oil has been shown to promote joint comfort, brain health and inhibit inflammation to support joint and cardiovascular health. Astaxanthin, a red-orange carotenoid found naturally in microalgae and krill oil, is a powerful antioxidant that promotes optimal mitochondrial function, brain health and even skin health.,INGREDIENTS MATTER - Sourced using only the finest raw ingredients with the purity and potency your body deserves. The majority of our products are non-GMO, gluten-free and manufactured in the USA—and a Certificate of Analysis is available for every product we produce.,LIVE YOUR HEALTHIEST LIFE - For over 40 years, we’ve been developing advanced, effective formulas made with the highest standards and based on the latest scientific findings. We believe the answers to a healthier, richer life are within reach, and that rigorous scientific research is the path to get us there. Our formulations are created using the ingredients and dosages used in the studies that inspired them, ensuring that maximum bioavailability and efficacy is achieved.

Our krill oil is sustainable sourced and fresh harvested from krill that thrive deep in their remote, natural habitat.,CLEAN SOURCED - As one of the world’s most isolated and pristine environments, the Antarctic is an ideal source for pure, clean krill oil that is free of environmental toxins, PCB’s, heavy metals and other contaminants. No GMO’s, artificial flavors, colors, or preservatives and no fishy aftertaste.,NUTRIENT RICH - Antler Farms Antarctic Krill Oil is an abundant source of essential omega 3 fatty acids, including EPA and DHA, phospholipids, and astaxanthin, a potent antioxidant. It also contains a variety of vitamins and minerals.,PROCESSED FOR PURITY - Our krill oil is extracted, filtered, and purified on location. The high speed of processing from ocean to facility results in a product that is exceptionally fresh, naturally bioactive and nutritionally complete.,POWERFUL BENEFITS - Antler Farms Antarctic Krill Oil contains active, fast absorbing nutrients that can optimize overall wellness. It supports healthy function of the brain, heart, joints and immune system. Krill oil also has antioxidant components.

name: Simply as-is | 500mg Antarctic Krill Oil | 60 Softgels | Phospholipid Bound Omega-3s EPA & DHA | Naturally High in Powerful Antioxidant Astaxanthin | No Fishy Reflux
feature_bullets: RICH IN OMEGA-3s: Krill oil contains unique phospholipid-bound EPA & DHA, which are beneficial essential fatty acids. Our krill oil has one of the highest levels of phospholipids on the market.,SUPPORTS COGNITIVE, JOINT + HEART HEALTH: Phospholipid-bound DHA and EPA supports maintenance of joint health and cardiovascular health. Krill oil also contains phosphatidyl choline for healthy brain function.,RICH IN ASTAXANTHIN FOR FREE-RADICAL PROTECTION: Contains naturally occurring astaxanthin which is the potent antioxidant that gives krill oil its vibrant red color and helps protect the cells in your body from free radical damage.,BETTER ABSORPTION + NO FISHY REFLUX: Phospholipids increase the bioavailability of omegas, so a smaller quantity of krill oil can deliver high levels of DHA and EPA in your body. The high phospholipid content of our krill oil also helps with better digestion of the oil, preventing those dreaded fishy burps.,SUSTAINABLY SOURCED: Collected from the pristine waters of the Antarctic using responsible practices focused on protecting the krill biomass and Antarctic eco-system.

name: Kori Antarctic Krill Oil Omega-3 800mg Supplement - Superior Absorption vs Fish Oil/EPA & DHA, Astaxanthin/Supports Heart, Brain, Joint, Eye, & Skin Health / 90 softgels
feature_bullets: THE OCEAN’S SUPERIOR OMEGA: Our sustainably sourced krill oil is a source clinically proven to raise the Omega-3 levels our bodies need and, coupled with other naturally occurring nutrients found in Antarctic krill, it delivers a powerful supplement designed to support heart, brain, joint, eye & skin health.,MOST NATURAL OMEGA-3 FORM: Kori delivers Omega-3s in their most natural phospholipid and triglyceride form, just as you get in a healthy fish diet, for SUPERIOR ABSORPTION vs fish oils and NO FISHY AFTERTASTE. This is because our bodies’ cells already are made of phospholipids so they absorb and digest this form best. Surprisingly, fish oils have triglycerides but lose phospholipids during processing.,NATURALLY MORE NUTRIENTS: Kori is packed full of esential EPA & DHA omega-3 fatty acids and is a natural source of the ESSENTIAL NUTRIENT CHOLINE, found in foods such as eggs and broccoli, for brain and nervous system health. Kori also has the POWERFUL ANTIOXIDANT ASTAXANTHIN.,CERTIFIED SUSTAINABLE: From the #1 global krill oil supplier that is the only global fishery to earn an ‘A’ rating, and for seven years running.,HARNESSING KRILL’S NUTRTION: Krill are at the start of the marine food chain and offer immense nutritional benefits. Advanced harvesting operations help preserve our krill oil quality. Kori is made with non-GMO krill oil & no artificial flavors, colors, or preservatives, unlike many fish oils that require added preservatives or added flavors to hide fishy tastes.

Krill Healthy Joint Formula also includes hyaluronic acid to lubricate and cushion against the repeated physical impacts of everyday life and is fortified with astaxanthin for additional support for joint comfort and range of motion.,ONE AND DONE – When it comes to promoting your joint health, we're guessing you don't want to interrupt your routine. Luckily, all it takes is one softgel a day to get all of these joint health-promoting ingredients. And did we mention that they are clinically studied? In one trial, participants began to experience relief from joint discomfort in just 7-14 days, just enough time to schedule your next adventure!,INGREDIENTS MATTER - Sourced using only the finest raw ingredients with the purity and potency your body deserves. This product is certified non-GMO and gluten-free. Manufactured in the USA and a Certificate of Analysis is available for every product we produce.,LIVE YOUR HEALTHIEST LIFE - For over 40 years, we’ve been developing advanced, effective formulas made with the highest standards and based on the latest scientific findings. We believe the answers to a healthier, richer life are within reach and that rigorous scientific research is the path to get us there. Our formulations are created using the exact ingredients and dosages used in the studies that inspired them, ensuring that maximum bioavailability and efficacy are achieved.

name: Oceanutra 100% Pure Antarctic Krill Oil, Organic Next Gen Omega 3 EPA/DHA, Sustainable & Traceable (1000mg Capsule, 60-Day Supply)
feature_bullets: Omega-3 Support | Made with the highly concentrated SuperbaBoost, Next Generation Krill Oil, Oceanutra Krill Oil is 100% Pure Wild-Caught Krill Oil and has very high Phospholipid levels at 56% (PL56). Even higher than Superba 2, which is 40% and some others claim to be krill oil, their levels can be as low as 5% which typically means they are blends and are predominantly fish oil. Look for 100% Pure Krill Oil and avoid the digestive issues often associated with fish oil.,PL 56 | More Phospholipids and Choline | Phospholipids make up 56% of Oceanutra Pure Krill Oil and also represent the building blocks of cell membranes in the body and therefore effectively deliver EPA and DHA to the blood, tissues and organs almost immediately. Supplementing the diet with Pure krill oil contributes to choline intake, which in turn supports cell membrane function and contributes to normal liver function, as well as normal lipid and homocysteine metabolism.,EPA DHA play many roles in the human body. They promote a healthy heart and help maintain normal triglyceride and blood pressure levels. DHA in particular can contribute to normal brain function and eye health. Since the human body cannot efficiently make EPA and DHA on its own, it is important that these fatty acids are supplied through the diet. Watch out for others that claim to be high potency Omega 3s, but contain Ethyl Esters or rTG, which are synthetic (made in lab).,NO FISHY AFTERTASTE | Pure Krill's Phospholipid-bound omega-3 fatty acids are water dispersible, making them easier to digest than fish oil. Pure Krill Oil’s ability to be absorbed directly means that your body is getting a higher percentage of Omega 3s than other non-phospholipid bound products, which means you are getting more of the benefits you paid for. Don’t be fooled by others with misleading labels. Look for Pure Krill and confirm the phospholipid percentage makes sense. Look for PL56.,USA: Oil Extracted, Processed, Encapsulated and Bottled in the USA from Wild-Caught Antarctic Krill. New More Concentrated, Premium Formula | Just one soft gel a day. Each softgel contains 1000 mg of certified 100% pure, sustainable & traceable Antarctic Krill oil with more naturally occurring EPA, DHA, Phospholipids and Astaxanthin. Krill Oil has phospholipid bound omega 3s that are absorbed directly and not stored as fats like fish oil, which can be lost before entering the cell membrane.

name: VITALITOWN Antarctic Krill Oil 1000mg, with Omega-3s EPA & DHA, Antioxidant Astaxanthin, No Fishy Odor or Aftertaste, Support Brain, Heart, Eye Health, 60 Softgels
feature_bullets: Phospholipid-Bound Omega-3s with Astaxanthin: Our Krill Oil is cold pressed from pure Antarctic krill which is harvested in a sustainable way from the pristine waters, having far less potential for any toxins and industrial contamination. It is an ideal source of omega-3s (EPA & DHA) – essential fatty acids that our body does not produce on its own and must be consumed from diet or supplement. One serving provides 200 mg of EPA, 100 mg of DHA, 400 mg of phospholipds and 1500 mcg of astaxanthin.,High Bioavailability & No Fishy Aftertaste: Known as a fish oil alternative, krill oil boasts omega-3 fatty acids in their most natural phospholipid form, making them better absorbed by our body. Krill oil also contains powerful antioxidant astaxanthin and essential nutrient choline, these not found in fish oil. With two krill oil softgels daily, you reap more health benefits than your run-of-the-mill fish oil supplements.* No gross fishy aftertaste or burps that deters people from taking.,Brain, Heart, Eye & Joint Health Support*: Omega-3s are an integral part of cell membranes. Our body needs them to develop and function optimally in every stage of life. The consumption of EPA and DHA helps to support proper cognitive performance, maintain healthy blood lipid levels already within normal range, and promotes eye health.* The included astaxanthin in krill oil, the cause of red color, is responsible for reducing common types of oxidative stress and increasing joint mobility.*,All About Quality: Vitalitown Krill Oil is intended for both men and women free of artificial fillers, flavors, preservatives, and additives. All products are non-GMO, and contain no gluten, dairy, soy, egg, fish, tree nuts, or peanuts. Your satisfaction is our priority. We stand behind our products, no questions asked, no ifs, no ands, no buts. If there is any problem, just let us know and we'll do our best to make it right.,The Way To Vitality: Here in Vitalitown, we believe nutrition is an important part of feeling healthy, active, and energetic which defines Vitality. We have been committed to providing high-quality supplements curated for your unique needs, bridging the nutritional gap and adding a dash of vitality to your life. All our products are made in the USA and tested by third party for purity & potency to ensure that each and every bottle of Vitalitown products represents the highest standards.

High concentration of 340mg Omega-3s brings great ower to your achy, crunching knees, hips & shoulders.* Carried in phospholipids, our EPA/DHA at a perfect ratio 2:1 is easily utilized by your body, helping keep joints well-lubricated, reduce joint discomfort & promote sharper cognitive ability & better memory.*,Proudly Made in the USA: Our advanced strength formula is loaded with the highest grade & naturally sourced ingredients in a GMP certified facility in the USA. Doctor’s Recipes Krill Oil for men & women is 100% pure, natural, sustainable & NON-GMO with no soy, gluten and dairy.,Personal Choices, Professional Solutions: At Doctor’s Recipes, we believe the products and services should be done professionally and with enthusiasm. feature_bullets: THE OCEAN’S SUPERIOR OMEGA: Our sustainably sourced krill oil is a source clinically proven to raise the Omega-3 levels our bodies need and, coupled with other naturally occurring nutrients found in Antarctic krill, it delivers a powerful supplement designed to support heart, brain, joint, eye & skin health.,MOST NATURAL OMEGA-3 FORM: Kori delivers Omega-3s in their most natural phospholipid and triglyceride form, just as you get in a healthy fish diet, for SUPERIOR ABSORPTION vs fish oils and NO FISHY AFTERTASTE. This is because our bodies’ cells already are made of phospholipids so they absorb and digest this form best. Surprisingly, fish oils have triglycerides but lose phospholipids during processing.,NATURALLY MORE NUTRIENTS: Kori is packed full of esential EPA & DHA omega-3 fatty acids and is a natural source of the ESSENTIAL NUTRIENT CHOLINE, found in foods such as eggs and broccoli, for brain and nervous system health. Kori also has the POWERFUL ANTIOXIDANT ASTAXANTHIN.,CERTIFIED SUSTAINABLE: From the #1 global krill oil supplier that is the only global fishery to earn an ‘A’ rating, and for seven years running.,HARNESSING KRILL’S NUTRTION: Krill are at the start of the marine food chain and offer immense nutritional benefits. Advanced harvesting operations help preserve our krill oil quality. Kori is made with non-GMO krill oil & no artificial flavors, colors, or preservatives, unlike many fish oils that require added preservatives or added flavors to hide fishy tastes.

feature_bullets: ANTARCTIC KRILL OIL, RICH IN OMEGA-3s: BioEmblem's premium krill oil is sustainably harvested from the pristine waters of the Antarctic Ocean. Every softgel is non-GMO, gluten free, soy free, dairy free, and corn free. Renew Naturals Krill Oil is rich in omega-3s that benefit and promote the wellness of the heart, blood vessels, supports blood pressure and cholesterol levels already within a normal range, can help promote a regular heart rhythm and support normal blood clotting processes. Omega-3s can help keep the heart and arteries healthy.,BRAIN HEALTH - Renew Naturals Krill Oil is rich in Phospholipids, which are a superior source of omega-3s for brain tissue. This can be valuable in maintaining memory and cognitive functions, especially among the elderly. Adequate consumption of omega-3s is recommended to maintain memory performance and to reduce the risk of developing mild memory problems associated with aging.,BETTER SMELL, TASTE AND LOOK - Renew Naturals Krill Oil doesn't smell old and rancid (as many krill products do). NO fish burps, NO fishy aftertaste! Many other krill oils smell so bad because they are bad! Renew Naturals Krill Oil is the freshest and purest available and is a healthy, bright red color because this is how krill oil occurs in nature. This is real, fresh krill! 1000MG PER SERVING (2 softgels),WOMEN'S/FEMININE HEALTH/ASTAXANTHIN - our Krill Oil can help ease the symptoms of PMS, menstrual pains, cramps and menopause and may be the natural relief and help you need, without dangerous painkillers. Krill Oil contains naturally occurring Astaxanthin, one of nature's most powerful antioxidants, and supports brain health, nervous system health, and helps to prevent krill oil from going rancid and smelly. Most omega-3 products - including fish oil - do not contain Astaxanthin.,100% MONEY-BACK SATISFACTION GUARANTEED & NO LEAKY CAPSULES! - Guaranteed you'll like it or your money back. Renew Naturals Krill Oil comes with a 90 Day NO Questions Asked 100% MONEY BACK GUARANTEE and the best customer service. Give us a try, we take all the risk, so Click ‘Add to Cart’ and see for yourself!

name: LABO Nutrition Perfect Krill EX, The Purest Ultra Strength Antarctic Krill Oil, Highest Phospholipids (>56%), with Choline & Astaxanthin, Omega 3, Joint Support, 100% Made in USA, 60 softgel
feature_bullets: SUPERIOR QUALITY, 100% PURE ANTARCTIC KRILL OIL: PERFECT KRILL EX is extracted with patented technology to increases the relative amount of phospholipids and choline (a quality marker of krill oil product), removes unwanted salts in the krill oil, which can otherwise result in off-odours and taste, and increases potential health benefits. It made PERFECT KRILL EX more potent and superior than regular krill oil.,ABOUT 3X MORE PHOSPHOLIPIDS, 2X MORE BIOAVAILABILITY AND EFFECTIVE: Krill oil is carried to your body's cells in phospholipid form, they are easily recognized, incorporated and utilized by your body. The majority of the omega3 in PERFECT KRILL EX are bound to phospholipids (More than 56% of Phospholipids), hence they are naturally 2 times more effectively absorbed by the body cells than fish oil supplement. Phospholipids content in PERFECT KRILL EX is 3 times more than regular krill oi.,PHARMACEUTICAL GRADE, EXTRA STRENGTH, OMEGA-3 ENHANCED: PERFECT KRILL EX is a highly concentrated krill oil rich in Omega-3 fatty acids EPA and DHA, as well as Phospholipids and Choline, well protected by the naturally powerful antioxidant, Astaxanthin. The natural component of astaxanthin in krill oil helps maintain freshness and stability without the need for preservatives. Extra strength soft gels provide 500mg per pure krill oil per softgel.,HEALTH BENEFITS/BACKED BY MORE THAN 80 PATENTS WORLDWIDE: support healthy liver and joints, helps to support healthy blood pressure, support a healthy menstrual cycle for women.,SAFE AND EASY TO SWALLOW/DIGEST: Heavy Metal Tested, Non GMO, Gluten Free. Phospholipids make krill oil’s omega-3s more easy to absorb, smaller softgel make it easy to swallow. No fishy aftertaste. 100% MADE IN USA

name: Life Extension Super Omega-3 Plus EPA/DHA Fish Oil, Sesame Lignans, Olive Extract, Krill & Astaxanthin - Heart, Brain & Joint Health Support - Gluten-Free, Non-GMO - 120 Softgels
feature_bullets: A FRESH & PURE FISH OIL - Our formula is made with a wild fish oil concentrate derived from South Pacific Ocean anchovy. It's caught and processed within hours of harvest in a marine mammal-friendly fishery in Chile.,GOOD FOR HEART & MIND - You'll get optimal doses of EPA and DHA omega-3 fatty acids with our formula, which supports cardiovascular and cognitive health. But that's just the beginning. We were inspired by the Mediterranean diet, which is associated with heart health and an increased life span. So we also include potent olive polyphenols and sesame lignans for additional health benefits.,KRILL OIL & ASTAXANTHIN - Our formula offers even more benefits with krill oil and astaxanthin. In clinical studies, krill oil has been shown to promote joint comfort, brain health and inhibit inflammation to support joint and cardiovascular health. Astaxanthin, a red-orange carotenoid found naturally in microalgae and krill oil, is a powerful antioxidant that promotes optimal mitochondrial function, brain health and even skin health.,INGREDIENTS MATTER - Sourced using only the finest raw ingredients with the purity and potency your body deserves. The majority of our products are non-GMO, gluten-free and manufactured in the USA—and a Certificate of Analysis is available for every product we produce.,LIVE YOUR HEALTHIEST LIFE - For over 40 years, we’ve been developing advanced, effective formulas made with the highest standards and based on the latest scientific findings. We believe the answers to a healthier, richer life are within reach, and that rigorous scientific research is the path to get us there. Our formulations are created using the ingredients and dosages used in the studies that inspired them, ensuring that maximum bioavailability and efficacy is achieved.
